    "instructions": [
      "The planner should identify the relevant concepts from the query and compose arithmetic at runtime.",
      "The ontology should not contain benchmark-specific metric families such as debt burden ratio or R and D ratio.",
      "Composite metrics should be assembled by the planner from concepts plus generic operations like ratio, difference, growth_rate, and sum."
    ]
  },
